- `_accepts_of(recs, closure, bdir)`: yields records in closure with decision=accept, matching sha256(canon(body))==rid, and subject parsed as JSON blob. Good.

- `_under_is(body, profile_hash, threshold_hash)`: checks under has len 2 and set(u) == {profile_hash, threshold_hash}. Good.

